FLEXIBLE AREAS FROM 600SQM - 1,100SQM 

On behalf of our client CBRE are pleased to offer for lease an A Grade office facility located within the Jandakot Business Park known as Jandakot City.

CBRE see this offering as an extremely rare opportunity for a business to lease First Class commercial buildings of the highest standard.

Flexibility is the key with this offering with various sizes available to suit a variety of needs.

Businesses can lease a smaller portion with the ability to grow in the future.

LOCATION 
Just 15 minutes from the Perth CBD, via the Kwinana Freeway and Roe Highway, Jandakot City is ideally located for ease of access for tenants and their customers.

Jandakot City is located at the entrance to Jandakot Airport and both precincts operate independently of each other. There is direct access off Roe Highway onto Karel Avenue which leads into Jandakot City from the east and north east suburbs, as well as easy entry onto the Kwinana Freeway (1km) which is the main north / south road transport route.


The vision for Jandakot City is an integrated commercial and industrial park occupied by high calibre tenants residing in first rate buildings owned by Jandakot City.


Please contact the exclusive agent to obtain further details and inspection.

Building A: 1,948sqm*
Building B: 1,340sqm*
Total: 3,288sqm*

- 4G Optus network

- Air conditioned throughout
- Great incentives offered
- End of trip facilities
- Ample parking
- Prime location with excellent exposure
- Excellent signage rights

Just 15 minutes from the Perth CBD, Jandakot City is ideally located for ease of access for tenants and their customers. Jandakot City is located at the entrance to Jandakot Airport and although both precincts operate independently access / exit points are shared. 

Importantly there is direct access off Roe Highway into the site from east and north east suburbs, as well as easy entry onto the Kwinana Freeway, the main north/south road transport route. An additional road link (Spartan Road) has been created to Berrigan Drive being “left in and left out”. The recently opened “south link” road provides an additional access / exit to Kwinana Freeway via Berrigan Drive. Likewise excellent access is available to Kewdale/Welshpool via Roe Highway (15 minutes). 

Karel Avenue being the main entrance has been upgraded to a dual carriageway boulevard with landscaping, extending into the centre of the development. 

Facilities at Jandakot City include:
- Supermarket
- Cafe
- Fast Food
- Pharmacy
- Liquor Shop
- 24 Hour Gym
- Medical Centre
- Regular Public Transport Services; and 
- Fuel Station (coming soon).

5 Compass Road is located within the in-demand Jandakot City business park, a circa 80 hectare precinct surrounding Jandakot Airport and occupied by a selection of major national and international logistics and oil and gas related businesses.  5 Compass Road is located 6kms* from the established Canning Vale industrial precinct and has access to the greater Perth metropolitan area via the soon to be upgraded Roe Highway/Kwinana Freeway interchange.  The Perth CBD is located 20kms* north of the property with the Fremantle Port located 17kms* west of the property.

5 Compass Road was purpose built some 8 years ago for Viridian Glass to house their glass manufacturing, distribution and administration functions servicing the WA market. This large high specification facility comprises 895sqm* of “A” grade office accommodation, 12,530sqm* of high specification warehouse and workshop serviced by multiple 3-6.8T gantry cranes with the balance of site providing excellent access and building circulation with parking for 85 cars*.
